  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div><div><p>At 20th level, your presence on the field of battle is an inspiration to those dedicated to your cause. You can use your bonus action to gain the following benefits for 1 hour:</p><ul><li>You have resistance to bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage.</li><li>You have advantage on any creature that has failed their saving throw against your Champion Challenge.</li><li>When you deal damage with Divine Smite the target must make a Wisdom saving throw against your Champion Challenge.</li></ul><p>Once you use this feature, you cannot use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p></div></div>",
